# close-brace-word-after

## Input

```
s {
  }value
}

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..15
  PREFIX_BLOCK@0..15
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "s"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{"
    NEWLINE@3..4 "\n"
    SPACE@4..6 "  "
    ENTRY@6..12
      WORD_KEY@6..12
        WORD@6..12 "}value"
    NEWLINE@12..13 "\n"
    CLOSE_BRACE@13..14 "}"
    NEWLINE@14..15 "\n"
```

## Syntax Error

```
[
    SyntaxError {
        message: "missing value for the key",
        range: 12..12,
    },
]
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        PrefixBlock {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "s",
            },
            open_brace: OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{",
            items: [
                Entry {
                    key: WordKey {
                        word: WORD@6..12 "}value",
                    },
                    value: none,
                },
            ],
            close_brace: CLOSE_BRACE@13..14 "}",
        },
    ],
}
```

